content: Sorry, I didn't explain fully. I told you my goal was to be an expert in AI, you told me to do these x things that would help me become an expert, which was connecting with thought leaders and doing projects and documenting them. You guided me to make that happen it what would seem is a very successful way. A best selling author liking and commenting your post and having the cold outreach you set up result in that connection and the mindset shift going forward and revised 60 hour days plan to focus on this project and see how far AI can take me is so sweet I think.
